308
00:17:20.996 --> 00:17:25.696
By the way, you made the ice wheels using the locked freezer!

309
00:17:25.696 --> 00:17:29.696
You stood a can of laver in the center of a toy pool

310
00:17:29.696 --> 00:17:32.796
