311
00:17:32.796 --> 00:17:34.896
to make two wheels, didn't you?

312
00:17:34.896 --> 00:17:38.096
You took the ice wheels from the freezer

313
00:17:38.096 --> 00:17:41.396
then rolled them over to the stairs so...

314
00:17:41.396 --> 00:17:43.696
the flour that Ran and Kazuha spilled on the floor

315
00:17:43.696 --> 00:17:47.196
wiped off leaving a track just the width of the wheels behind.

316
00:17:47.196 --> 00:17:49.596
Gosh, these kids have the nerve

317
00:17:49.596 --> 00:17:51.696
