318
00:17:51.696 --> 00:17:54.596
You've got the proof, don't you?

319
00:17:55.196 --> 00:17:59.396
You didn't delete Hakuya's mail from Hikaru's cell phone

320
00:17:59.396 --> 00:18:02.096
