333
00:18:37.296 --> 00:18:41.796
you killed her in self defense because she attacked you.

334
00:18:41.796 --> 00:18:45.296
So, if you placed the plan sheet next to Hikaru's corpse

335
00:18:45.296 --> 00:18:47.196
