338
00:18:53.796 --> 00:18:55.296
Darn.

339
00:18:55.296 --> 00:18:57.496
How'd these brats get to all this...

340
00:18:57.496 --> 00:19:00.096
It would've worked out well otherwise.

341
00:19:00.096 --> 00:19:03.296
We thought there was something fishy about you

